article_node.title: Innovative Solutions Announces Successful Use of DarcyIQ in Strategic Collaboration Agreement with AWS Focused on Smaller Businesses
article_node.summary: Innovative Solutions, a Premier Tier AWS Partner, announced milestones in its Strategic Collaboration Agreement with AWS to help SMBs grow on the cloud. The company leveraged its agentic AI consulting platform DarcyIQ to triple SMB customer acquisition in eight months and has expanded its Boca Raton headquarters, added products, and built technology enabling businesses to purchase AWS services directly. As a launch partner for AWS’s SMB Competency, Innovative offers expertise across manufacturing, retail, finance, and life sciences, and aims to be the trusted partner guiding SMBs through AWS’s ecosystem. The partnership includes AWS co‑investment in go‑to‑market activities and support for SMB customers, positioning Innovative at the forefront of generative AI and cloud modernization solutions for small and midsize businesses.
